high_descs: Turn around, take a step, turn right and walk across the room to the refrigerator.  Turn right at the refrigerator and walk forward to the dish washer in the middle of the room.  Turn left and face the dish washer.
Pick up the knife on the left next to the roll of paper towels.
Turn right, take a step and turn left to face the counter.
Slice the tomato.
Turn right and walk to the wall.  At the wall, turn left and face the counter.
Put the knife down in front of the keurig.
Turn left and walk forward to the middle of the room.  At the dish washer, turn right and face the counter.
Pick up the right end of the tomato.
Turn left and walk forward with the tomato slice to the front of the refrigerator.  Face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door and put the tomato slice in the refrigerator in between the egg and the apple toward the front of the shelf.  Close the door.  Open the door and grab the tomato slice.  Close the refrigerator door.
Turn right and walk to the other side of the room.  At the wall, turn left and face the counter in front of the keurig.
Put the tomato slice down to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato and cool it.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go past the island, to the refrigerator, then turn to your right and go to the counter top to your right, just past the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife directly in front of the loaf of bread, on the counter.
Move over to the right side of the counter, near the stove.
Cut the tomato on the back of the counter, to the left of the vase, into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the end of the counter, where the coffee maker is, on your right.
Place the knife on the drip pan of the coffee maker.
Turn to your left and go back to the stove where the tomato is on, past the stove, and to your right.
Pick up one of the tomato slices, on the counter.
Turn to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the tomato slice in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, between the apple and the egg, wait a moment for the tomato slice to chill, then remove the tomato from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the kitchen, then turn to the counter on your left, where the knife is.
Place the tomato on the counter to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a cold tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around then turn right move forward toward the fridge then turn right the turn left to face the kitchen counter.
Pick up the table knife on the left from the kitchen counter.
Carry the table knife and move to the right to reach the tomato on the kitchen counter.
Slice the tomato on the kitchen counter using the table knife.
Take table knife , turn to the right then left and face the kitchen counter.
Place knife next to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter.
Turn left, then turn to the right and face the kitchen counter
Pick up a slice of tomato
Take the slice of tomato turn around turn to the right then right again to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place sliced tomato onto the shelf in the fridge, close fridge door.
Open fridge door, take out sliced tomato from the shelf inside the fridge, close fridge door. Turn right toward the coffee maker then left and face the coffee maker on the kitchen counter.
Place sliced tomato onto kitchen counter next to the knife near the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Use the table knife to slice a tomato, place it next to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter.
